---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/main.astro';
import AssessmentQuiz from '../components/AssessmentQuiz';
---

<MainLayout pageClass="">
<div class="w-full min-h-screen rx-bg-deep-space">
<a href="#main-content" class="sr-only focus:not-sr-only focus:absolute focus:top-4 focus:left-4 focus:z-50 focus:px-4 focus:py-2 focus:bg-[#73B400] focus:text-[#0D1117] focus:rounded focus:font-bold">Skip to main content</a>
<div id="main-content" class="w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 sm:py-12 md:py-16">
<!-- Hero Section -->
<div class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16 sm:mb-20 text-center">
<!-- Logo -->
<div class="mb-8 sm:mb-12">
<img src="/reshapex-logo.svg" alt="ReshapeX" class="h-12 sm:h-16 w-auto mx-auto" style="display: block;" />
</div>

<!-- Headline -->
<div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
<h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black tracking-tight leading-tight">
<span class="rx-gradient-text rx-gc-green-yellow">
AI Readiness Assessment
</span>
</h1>
<p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl rx-text-steel leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
Discover how smarter AI agents can deliver better outcomes and faster revenue for your operations. Get your readiness score and see if you qualify for our full assessment.
</p>
</div>

<!-- Feature Pills -->
<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center mt-8 sm:mt-10 px-4">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-3 rounded-full rx-bg-slate border border-[rgba(139,154,173,0.2)] hover:border-[rgba(115,180,0,0.4)] transition-all duration-300">
<svg class="w-5 h-5 rx-text-green flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
</svg>
<span class="text-sm font-semibold rx-text-steel">Under 3 minutes</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-3 rounded-full rx-bg-slate border border-[rgba(139,154,173,0.2)] hover:border-[rgba(0,217,255,0.4)] transition-all duration-300">
<svg class="w-5 h-5 rx-text-blue flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
</svg>
<span class="text-sm font-semibold rx-text-steel">8 questions</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-3 rounded-full rx-bg-slate border border-[rgba(139,154,173,0.2)] hover:border-[rgba(115,180,0,0.4)] transition-all duration-300">
<svg class="w-5 h-5 rx-text-green flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
</svg>
<span class="text-sm font-semibold rx-text-steel">Instant diagnostic</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- Quiz Section -->
<div class="w-full mb-20">
<AssessmentQuiz client:only="react" />
</div>

<!-- What You'll Get Section -->
<div class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-16 sm:mb-20 px-4">
<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-center mb-8 sm:mb-12">
<span class="rx-gradient-text rx-gc-green-blue">What You'll Get</span>
</h2>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-6 items-stretch">
<!-- Score Card -->
<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-xl rx-bg-slate border border-[rgba(139,154,173,0.15)] hover:border-[#73B400] hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-[rgba(115,180,0,0.1)] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 h-full">
<div class="w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 rx-gradient-text rx-gc-green-yellow mb-4 sm:mb-6">
<svg class="w-8 h-8 sm:w-10 sm:h-10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
</svg>
</div>
<h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold mb-2 sm:mb-3 text-white">Readiness Score</h3>
<p class="text-sm rx-text-steel leading-relaxed">
Get your AI readiness score (0-100) and see if you qualify for our full assessment that identifies smarter agents, better outcomes, and faster revenue opportunities.
</p>
</div>

<!-- Diagnostic Card -->
<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-xl rx-bg-slate border border-[rgba(139,154,173,0.15)] hover:border-[#00D9FF] hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-[rgba(0,217,255,0.1)] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 h-full">
<div class="w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 rx-gradient-text rx-gc-blue-white mb-4 sm:mb-6">
<svg class="w-8 h-8 sm:w-10 sm:h-10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2" />
</svg>
</div>
<h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold mb-2 sm:mb-3 text-white">Quick Diagnostic</h3>
<p class="text-sm rx-text-steel leading-relaxed">
Identify high-level opportunities where smarter AI agents could improve outcomes and accelerate revenue in your operations.
</p>
</div>

<!-- Next Steps Card -->
<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-xl rx-bg-slate border border-[rgba(139,154,173,0.15)] hover:border-[#FF006E] hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-[rgba(255,0,110,0.1)] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 h-full">
<div class="w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 rx-gradient-text rx-gc-magenta-green mb-4 sm:mb-6">
<svg class="w-8 h-8 sm:w-10 sm:h-10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
</svg>
</div>
<h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold mb-2 sm:mb-3 text-white">Next Steps</h3>
<p class="text-sm rx-text-steel leading-relaxed">
If you qualify, book a full assessment where we'll build, tune, and maintain AI agents tailored to your operations.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- Why Full Assessment Section -->
<div class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16 sm:mb-20 px-4">
<div class="p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10 rounded-xl rx-bg-slate border-2 border-[rgba(115,180,0,0.3)] relative overflow-hidden hover:border-[rgba(115,180,0,0.5)] transition-all duration-300">
<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5 pointer-events-none">
<div class="rx-animated-gradient w-full h-full"></div>
</div>
<div class="relative z-10 text-center space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
<h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">
<span class="rx-gradient-text rx-gc-green-blue">Why a Full Assessment?</span>
</h3>
<p class="text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg rx-text-steel leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
This quick assessment identifies high-level opportunities. Our full 30-45 minute assessment goes deeper: 
we'll identify where smarter AI agents can deliver better outcomes and faster revenue, then provide a complete 
plan for building, tuning, and maintaining them for your operations.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- Footer -->
<div class="w-full text-center px-4">
<p class="text-sm rx-text-steel">
Â© 2024 <span class="rx-text-green font-semibold">ReshapeX</span>. Built to help organizations evaluate their AI automation readiness.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</MainLayout>
